ica y eficiencia. Si busca confiabilidad en metalurgia, est en el lugar correcto.</p>\",\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">The metalworking industry is constantly evolving, and our company keeps up with every step of this transformation. We work with <strong>high-quality metal sheets</strong>, providing customized solutions for different sectors, from civil construction to the automotive industry.</p><h3 style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Why choose our solutions?</h3><p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Precision in sheet cutting and bending</p><p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Specialized and experienced team</p><p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Advanced technology in production processes</p><p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Commitment to deadlines and quality</p><p style=\\\"text-align:start;\\\">Our goal is to transform raw materials into <em>lasting results</em>, combining strength, aesthetics, and efficiency. If you are looking for reliability in metalworking, you are in the right place.</p>\"}',NULL,'post',NULL,1,NULL,'publish',NULL,'2025-09-02 19:40:44','2025-09-02 19:43:26','2025-09-04 18:39:55',NULL);
